CellSociety.Grids

Interface SimulationGrid<E extends Abstract_Cell<E,T>,T extends AbstractDiscrete_CellState<T,? extends java.lang.Enum<?>>>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - Type of Abstract_Cell contained by the grid
    T - Type of AbstractDiscrete_CellState contained by the Cells of the grid Created by th174 on 2/12/2017.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimulationGridImpl

    public interface SimulationGrid<E extends Abstract_Cell<E,T>,T extends AbstractDiscrete_CellState<T,? extends java.lang.Enum<?>>>
    Interface provides basic API for a Grid of Abstract_Cells with Abstract_CellStates to run the simulation on
